[
  {
    "startTime": 0.036,
    "endTime": 2.354,
    "text": "[Woman Host] What does a family dinner look like in your house?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.374,
    "endTime": 5.427,
    "text": "Most of the time we eat out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.427,
    "endTime": 6.119,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.319,
    "endTime": 6.997,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Do you like eating out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.097,
    "endTime": 10.899000000000001,
    "text": "Yes, way better than home-cooked meals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.899,
    "endTime": 14.232,
    "text": "(bright, playful music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.537,
    "endTime": 22.058999999999997,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Miko, notice anything unusual?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.059,
    "endTime": 23.512,
    "text": "I have a second chair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.512,
    "endTime": 24.581,
    "text": "Hi, chair!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.781,
    "endTime": 26.563,
    "text": "[Woman Host] What do you think you're doing today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.663,
    "endTime": 29.123,
    "text": "Saying hi to a chair and give him cash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.123,
    "endTime": 30.022000000000002,
    "text": "[Woman Host] You are wrong!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.022,
    "endTime": 30.955,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.255,
    "endTime": 31.994,
    "text": "[Woman Host] What do you think that's there for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.294,
    "endTime": 33.32299999999999,
    "text": "My daddy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.323,
    "endTime": 34.587,
    "text": "[Woman Host] You got that right!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.587,
    "endTime": 36.492000000000004,
    "text": "My mom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.492,
    "endTime": 38.605999999999995,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.606,
    "endTime": 39.816,
    "text": "How's it going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.816,
    "endTime": 40.449000000000005,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.449,
    "endTime": 41.994,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Cavalli, tell me a little about your mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.994,
    "endTime": 43.554,
    "text": "She's beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.554,
    "endTime": 44.68,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Awwww."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.78,
    "endTime": 46.03,
    "text": "Thank you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.93,
    "endTime": 48.78,
    "text": "[Woman Host] What do you think your mom was like when she was your age?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.8,
    "endTime": 51.524,
    "text": "Okay, she was boring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.524,
    "endTime": 52.797000000000004,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Mari, is this true?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.797,
    "endTime": 54.721999999999994,
    "text": "Emmmm...no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.722,
    "endTime": 55.487,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.487,
    "endTime": 56.808,
    "text": "[Woman Host] We're doing a special episode"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.808,
    "endTime": 59.737,
    "text": "where it's stuff that your mom ate when she was little."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.737,
    "endTime": 61.136,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.136,
    "endTime": 62.169000000000004,
    "text": "You excited?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.169,
    "endTime": 62.501999999999995,
    "text": "Mm Hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.502,
    "endTime": 64.287,
    "text": "You wanna see what it is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.287,
    "endTime": 65.497,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Do you have any guesses what it might be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.497,
    "endTime": 66.907,
    "text": "Cupcakes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.907,
    "endTime": 67.955,
    "text": "That's all I know!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.955,
    "endTime": 71.096,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Alright. Well, let's close your eyes and find out. - 'Cause I forgot everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.013,
    "endTime": 73.17,
    "text": "Yeah, yeah cupcakes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.17,
    "endTime": 75.796,
    "text": "Really? They look like cupcakes to you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.796,
    "endTime": 78.774,
    "text": "Watch. Can I have some whipped cream?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.774,
    "endTime": 82.07900000000001,
    "text": "(laughs) [Woman Host] What?! No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.371,
    "endTime": 84.271,
    "text": "Aw...beans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.112,
    "endTime": 86.044,
    "text": "You ate beans?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.044,
    "endTime": 91.958,
    "text": "Chicken in a Biskit, sardines, Tabasco and then, cheese whiz."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.024,
    "endTime": 95.352,
    "text": "Take this, fill it all the way up,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.352,
    "endTime": 98.242,
    "text": "take one of the cookies, drop it in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.242,
    "endTime": 101.254,
    "text": "Sometimes you need to push it down with one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.254,
    "endTime": 102.962,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.962,
    "endTime": 106.313,
    "text": "- Oh my, that looks disgusting. - So this is a piece of the sardine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.175,
    "endTime": 107.71,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Cavalli, have you ever had sardines before?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.81,
    "endTime": 108.47800000000001,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.478,
    "endTime": 110.11099999999999,
    "text": "- Ooh. - You have to shake it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.146,
    "endTime": 111.871,
    "text": "Ooh, is that okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.871,
    "endTime": 112.80799999999999,
    "text": "I love it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.808,
    "endTime": 114.04100000000001,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.264,
    "endTime": 120.76299999999999,
    "text": "You can cut the potatoes in small pieces."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.763,
    "endTime": 121.796,
    "text": "Are you really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.796,
    "endTime": 122.72500000000001,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.025,
    "endTime": 123.75800000000001,
    "text": "There."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.758,
    "endTime": 129.091,
    "text": "Okay, so what you do, put the beans inside the Pandesal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.097,
    "endTime": 133.013,
    "text": "More than that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.213,
    "endTime": 133.93,
    "text": "Keep going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.931,
    "endTime": 135.764,
    "text": "Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.823,
    "endTime": 138.656,
    "text": "Good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.656,
    "endTime": 139.93,
    "text": "Try one of these."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.93,
    "endTime": 141.73600000000002,
    "text": "And the trick with this is you want it to get..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.736,
    "endTime": 143.783,
    "text": "Uh-oh. See that's what happens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.783,
    "endTime": 146.768,
    "text": "So you gotta find the perfect time where it's super soft,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.768,
    "endTime": 148.968,
    "text": "but won't fall or break."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.01,
    "endTime": 153.351,
    "text": "That was a perfect dip."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.951,
    "endTime": 155.85,
    "text": "It's not the best thing in the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.85,
    "endTime": 157.06,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.06,
    "endTime": 158.256,
    "text": "[Woman Host] What if you could make this better, Wren?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.256,
    "endTime": 159.631,
    "text": "Chocolate syrup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.631,
    "endTime": 162.142,
    "text": "That's not a bad idea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.042,
    "endTime": 163.072,
    "text": "Oh man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.172,
    "endTime": 167.155,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Kids these days, am I right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.022,
    "endTime": 168.753,
    "text": "Better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.753,
    "endTime": 169.72199999999998,
    "text": "Try it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.722,
    "endTime": 170.955,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.238,
    "endTime": 176.582,
    "text": "Very potato-ish in that dish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.582,
    "endTime": 177.797,
    "text": "Okay, ready?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.797,
    "endTime": 180.947,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Three, two, one..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.664,
    "endTime": 188.756,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.756,
    "endTime": 189.589,
    "text": "Oh no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.795,
    "endTime": 191.32,
    "text": "Really!?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.32,
    "endTime": 193.142,
    "text": "That taste disgusting!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.142,
    "endTime": 196.436,
    "text": "Well, it was great! I don't know what he talking 'bout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.436,
    "endTime": 198.82,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.82,
    "endTime": 199.912,
    "text": "Mmm..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.912,
    "endTime": 201.223,
    "text": "How's it taste?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.323,
    "endTime": 202.05200000000002,
    "text": "Good!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.052,
    "endTime": 204.916,
    "text": "'Kay. Imagine eating this everyday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.916,
    "endTime": 206.701,
    "text": "Why did you eat this everyday?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.801,
    "endTime": 208.16,
    "text": "We were broke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.16,
    "endTime": 213.202,
    "text": "Growing up in Colombia, we stay at a table and we no leave the table 'til we are finished."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.385,
    "endTime": 216.93699999999998,
    "text": "Here, trying to raise four kids has been hard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.937,
    "endTime": 218.64100000000002,
    "text": "I try to do my best."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.2,
    "endTime": 534.589,
    "text": "In my country, you grab a potato, and then, put some wasabi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.589,
    "endTime": 535.7600000000001,
    "text": "- [Woman Host] What country is this? - The brain country."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.76,
    "endTime": 544.17,
    "text": "Oh, the brain country."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.17,
    "endTime": 554.03,
    "text": "I bet you wanted me to feed this to my kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.03,
    "endTime": 560.769,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Cavalli, do you think you're gonna do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.769,
    "endTime": 569.03,
    "text": "Nope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.03,
    "endTime": 571.579,
    "text": "Not even the crackers and the cheese?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.579,
    "endTime": 579.1999999999999,
    "text": "I'll give them that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.2,
    "endTime": 582.2900000000001,
    "text": "Maybe I'll sneak a little of Tabasco on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.29,
    "endTime": 587.05,
    "text": "[Woman Host] Wren, do you think you could see yourself making this at home?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.05,
    "endTime": 591.12,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.12,
    "endTime": 599.839,
    "text": "Cheers to making this at home!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.839,
    "endTime": 606.36,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.36,
    "endTime": 609.86,
    "text": "It's pretty good, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.86,
    "endTime": 618.8100000000001,
    "text": "Mh hm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.81,
    "endTime": 624.27,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.27,
    "endTime": 630.18,
    "text": "I just showed my daughter this incredible recipe that I came up with and that you love, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.18,
    "endTime": 634.9899999999999,
    "text": "Does anybody else eat this? Comment below!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.99,
    "endTime": 647.1,
    "text": "You say thank you for watching."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.1,
    "endTime": 646.1800000000001,
    "text": "Thank you for watching!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.18,
    "endTime": 652.3389999999999,
    "text": "Goodbye!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.339,
    "endTime": 660.149,
    "text": "Bye."
  }
]